 pieces","10 g fresh parsley, leaves only","100 g red onions, quartered","50 g wheat germ","25 g olive oil, plus extra for frying","fresh spinach leaves, to serve"]}],"id":"r134394","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-hVkAFfupk_s\/XZVQbyd45SI\/AAAAAAAAdBA\/EiJQBucw9EgcIvYCUMmtGggK5XQ3WmlfACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_NI2cQmPv2VDgzxsY.png","title":"Lentil Burgers with Beetroot Rolls and Vegan Mayonnaise","publishedAt":"2018-02-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"11 g","fat":"34 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"58 g","calories":"2473 kJ \/ 591 kcal"},"usefulItems":"jug, frying pan, refrigerator, hob","hintsAndTricks":["Lentils come in various colours including black, red, yellow and orange. Classified as legumes, they are high in fibre which is associated with lowering blood glucose and intestinal disorders."],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","4h 20m","10 pieces"]}